{"tid":1686880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實有冇辦法可以真正制裁黑警？","createTime":"2019-11-01T12:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T15:43:02.000Z","uid":248131,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa892797069e255e0c780638849ec65f4758cf9a","tid":1686880,"uid":248131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"宜家美國有人權法，仲有hk be water act，但係會唔會有其他辦法可以真正制裁班賤賊，令佢地受審？<br />\n<br />\n之前有個巴打提出我地要令英美國際宣告廢除中英聯合聲明，並宣告中共非法佔領香港，從而令英美派兵駐港，令香港成為中立地區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqwG4YP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqwG4YP.jpg&h=b2a8cafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有冇方法可以令英美廢除中英聯合聲明同駐軍香港後，正式廢除現有警隊，將佢地歸為直屬中國嘅組織，令佢地帶上軍事法庭受審？</span><br />\n<br />\n之前有睇過其他巴打話戰爭罪行係需要國與國之間先會成立，唔知道如果香港成為中立地區之後算唔算一個獨立個體，到時就會變相係香港對中共，咁就符合戰爭罪嘅範圍<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁樣會唔會可行，希望巴打可以解答，小弟對呢啲唔係好熟，只係忽發奇想，有錯請見諒"},{"pid":"cea1b17170f87586f92eea7e2b695e3adc19851f","tid":1686880,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署 】依個就快截止⚠️<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=bf370f76\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=995a7e91\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n簽&gt;記得email確認&gt;傳開去"},{"pid":"7033dcd5c51d28f4d285e5dd8254b924ec58819c","tid":1686880,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"最直接咪打柒佢 不過香港有幾多人敢？"},{"pid":"c4fa8a0b43dbc20dcaf146db6d69f9044f591f87","tid":1686880,"uid":248131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7033dcd5c51d2